  "text": "Our work fits a growing tradition of computational work to better understand people based on their online behavior. Much of this type of work uses human properties to better perform traditional computational linguistics tasks, while others focus particularly on predicting user attributes. User network information has been used for tweet summarization or filtering [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
